Problem 1: String Length
Find length of a string.
class StringLength { public static void main(String[] args) { String s = "Java";
System.out.println(s.length()); } }
Problem 2: Reverse String
Reverse a string.
class ReverseString { public static void main(String[] args) { String s = "Java";
String rev = ""; for(int i = s.length()-1; i >= 0; i--) rev += s.charAt(i);
System.out.println(rev); } }